- "average size of the encoded videos" is the mean size of the videos encoded with each configuration;
- "overall score" is calculated as the product of the number of performance metrics and the average size of the encoded videos;
- The configurations are ranked in descending order of their overall scores.

- 'longer than a heartbeat' is a metaphorical way to say more than 10 minutes;
